{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "0.680", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich hoffe, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "0.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "3.600", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie bleiben noch einen kleinen Moment. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "6.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "12.440", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es geht mit diesem Thema noch ein kleines bisschen weiter."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "12.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "14.960", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrte Frau Pr\u00e4sidentin! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "14.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "17.400", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrte Damen und Herren! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "17.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "22.040", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die schon erw\u00e4hnten Aufnahmen aus der TV-Reportage \u201eGeheimsache Tiertransporte\u201c\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "22.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "23.000", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "so hie\u00df sie n\u00e4mlich\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "23.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "24.120", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "haben nicht nur mich schockiert, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "24.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "26.800", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern auch viele B\u00fcrgerinnen und B\u00fcrger\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "26.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "29.560", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "auch wenn jetzt nicht mehr so viele hier anwesend sind\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "29.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "30.600", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie sicherlich auch alle hier im Saal, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "30.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "32.360", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die nun zu Recht fordern, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "32.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "37.080", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "diese elenden Langstreckentransporte in au\u00dfereurop\u00e4ische Anrainerstaaten endlich zu beenden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "37.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "41.480", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch Vertreter der deutschen Landwirtschaft sehen das so und unterst\u00fctzen diese Forderung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "41.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "45.800", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist n\u00e4mlich auch zum Schaden der Landwirtschaft und nicht gut f\u00fcr ihr Image."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "45.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "51.080", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Welche Grausamkeiten unsere heimischen Tiere in ihren Ziell\u00e4ndern au\u00dferhalb der Europ\u00e4ischen Union erleiden m\u00fcssen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "51.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "52.960", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist nur schwer in Worte zu fassen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "52.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "57.240", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "So werden Rindern nach dem Entladen die Sehnen an den Beinen durchgetrennt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "57.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "58.720", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "damit sie nicht weglaufen k\u00f6nnen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "58.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "60.960", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "oder ihnen werden die Augen ausgestochen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "60.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "64.000", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "damit sie sich nicht orientieren und weglaufen k\u00f6nnen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "64.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "65.600", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nach einer tagelangen Fahrt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "65.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "67.640", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "eingepfercht im Lkw, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "67.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "70.480", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und der Maltr\u00e4tierung beim Entladen\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "70.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "74.320", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "beispielsweise werden die Tiere an einem Bein aufgeh\u00e4ngt und heruntergeworfen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "74.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "76.160", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weil das einfacher ist\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "76.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "80.880", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "werden unsere Tiere oft nicht artgerecht und ohne jede Bet\u00e4ubung geschlachtet. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "80.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "82.760", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das sind keine Einzelf\u00e4lle. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "82.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "84.560", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir alle sind uns einig\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "84.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "86.520", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das bringen auch die Antr\u00e4ge zum Ausdruck; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "86.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "87.640", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "daf\u00fcr bin ich dankbar\u00a0\u2013, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "87.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "93.200", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass dies nicht ansatzweise etwas mit unseren Grunds\u00e4tzen eines artgerechten Umgangs zu tun hat. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "93.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "99.200", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Insbesondere an der bulgarisch-t\u00fcrkischen Grenze kommt es immer wieder zu tierschutzrelevanten Problemen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "99.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "105.120", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "So leiden die Tiere aufgrund elend langer Wartezeiten h\u00e4ufig unter Hunger, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "105.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "107.760", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Durst und extremen Temperaturen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "107.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "110.520", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Viele Tiere \u00fcberstehen diese Tortur erst gar nicht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "110.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "112.360", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern verenden bereits vor der Ankunft. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "112.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "113.840", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist insbesondere bei Schlachttieren der Fall. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "113.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "116.520", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber diese Verluste sind einkalkuliert. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "116.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "119.800", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Beim Handeln besteht also schon unbedingter Vorsatz. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "119.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "121.320", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es ist im Plan."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "121.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "122.720", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wer nun denkt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "122.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "128.000", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass solche Tiertransporte nicht so h\u00e4ufig stattfinden und daher eine zu vernachl\u00e4ssigende Gr\u00f6\u00dfe sind, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "128.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "129.120", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "t\u00e4uscht sich. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "129.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "134.720", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Von 2013 bis 2016 hat sich die Anzahl der Rindertransporte in den Libanon verdreifacht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "134.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "136.800", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in die T\u00fcrkei sogar verzehnfacht. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "136.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "140.360", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Gab es 2013 rund 90\u00a0Rindertransporte, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "140.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "143.160", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "waren es 2016 fast 1\u00a0000. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "143.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "145.040", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch die durchschnittliche Transportdauer hat sich erh\u00f6ht. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "145.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "148.400", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Lag sie 2013 noch um die 42\u00a0Stunden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "148.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "151.400", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "waren es 2016\u00a0 70\u00a0Stunden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "151.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "152.720", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es dauert also l\u00e4nger. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "152.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "155.320", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Damit verl\u00e4ngern sich auch die Qualen der Tiere. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "155.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "159.960", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Anstatt unsere Tiere sehenden Auges auf eine lange und oft grausam endende Reise zu schicken, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "159.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "160.960", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sollten die Tiere\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "160.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "162.560", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das wurde schon vorgeschlagen\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "162.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "167.120", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "lieber in Deutschland tierschutzgerecht geschlachtet und dann das gefrorene Fleisch transportiert werden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "167.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "172.280", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir diskutieren beim Tierschutz \u00fcber Haltungsbedingungen und alle m\u00f6glichen Verbesserungen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "172.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "174.080", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Stichwort \u201eTierwohl\u201c. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "174.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "180.120", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber hier werden sehenden Auges seit Jahr und Tag derartige Transporte in Kauf genommen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "180.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "181.240", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "nach dem Motto: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "181.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "183.480", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Da das im Ausland stattfindet, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "183.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "185.200", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "brauchen wir uns nicht zu k\u00fcmmern."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "185.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "187.360", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wie im Antrag der Gr\u00fcnen richtigerweise festgestellt wird, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "187.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "192.160", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "hat der Europ\u00e4ische Gerichtshof bereits 2015 in einem Urteil bekr\u00e4ftigt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "192.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "196.560", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die europ\u00e4ischen Tierschutzstandards bis zum Bestimmungsort eingehalten werden m\u00fcssen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "196.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "200.520", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Tiere werden also nicht in einem rechtsfreien Raum transportiert. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "200.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "205.320", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ihr Wohl muss auch in au\u00dfereurop\u00e4ischen L\u00e4ndern sichergestellt werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "205.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "207.000", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Darum geht es in beiden Antr\u00e4gen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "207.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "208.200", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie gehen in die richtige Richtung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "208.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "208.960", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn Sie fordern, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "208.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "214.480", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "bei Nichteinhaltung unserer Standards den Lebendtiertransport in Drittstaaten zu stoppen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "214.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "221.000", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In den letzten Jahren wurde immer wieder eine \u00dcberarbeitung der europ\u00e4ischen Transportverordnung angek\u00fcndigt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "221.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "225.760", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Bundesminister Christian Schmidt hat sich zwar in Briefen an den zust\u00e4ndigen EU-Kommissar gewandt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "225.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "229.360", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Handfestes ist allerdings bislang nicht dabei herausgekommen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "229.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "233.440", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Anschreiben ersetzen nicht das tats\u00e4chliche T\u00e4tigwerden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "233.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "236.440", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Anschreiben reichen nicht aus. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "236.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "237.400", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sch\u00f6n ist zwar, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "237.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "240.760", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die EU-Kommission eine Tierschutzplattform eingerichtet hat, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "240.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "245.240", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wo eine Untergruppe speziell Vorlagen f\u00fcr Tierschutz und Tiertransporte erarbeiten soll. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "245.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "246.440", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber diese Untergruppe arbeitet noch nicht. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "246.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "250.320", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch hier ist eine zeitnahe Handlungsempfehlung nicht zu erwarten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "250.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "252.440", 
   "id": "s000083", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Alles scheint sich sehr lange hinzuziehen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "252.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "253.400", 
   "id": "s000084", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Positiv ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "253.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "263.160", 
   "id": "s000085", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass das Bundesministerium f\u00fcr Ern\u00e4hrung und Landwirtschaft eine Delegation des t\u00fcrkischen Landwirtschaftsministeriums zu einer gemeinsamen Besichtigung von deutschen Kontrollstellen eingeladen hat, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "263.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "270.000", 
   "id": "s000086", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "damit \u00e4hnliche Anlagen auch in der bulgarisch-t\u00fcrkischen Grenzregion gebaut und die Tiere besser versorgt werden k\u00f6nnen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "270.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "273.760", 
   "id": "s000087", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Hier braucht es aber konkrete Umsetzungszeitr\u00e4ume und eine Finanzierung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "273.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "275.840", 
   "id": "s000088", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nur Gucken reicht nicht. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "275.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "279.280", 
   "id": "s000089", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Insbesondere die EU-Kommission ist gefordert, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "279.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "283.760", 
   "id": "s000090", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "an Grenz \u00ad \u00fcberg\u00e4ngen zus\u00e4tzliche Kontrollpunkte und Einrichtungen zu installieren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "283.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "288.080", 
   "id": "s000091", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um die Wartezeiten zu verringern und die Tiere mit Futter und Wasser zu versorgen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "288.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "289.800", 
   "id": "s000092", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und das nicht nur an einer Stelle."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "289.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "293.080", 
   "id": "s000093", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Wille der EU-Mitgliedstaaten allerdings, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "293.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "297.600", 
   "id": "s000094", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ordnungsrechtliche Ver\u00e4nderungen an der europ\u00e4ischen Tierschutzverordnung vorzunehmen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "297.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "300.120", 
   "id": "s000095", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "war bislang \u00fcberhaupt nicht zu erkennen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "300.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "304.840", 
   "id": "s000096", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Interessen der Mitgliedstaaten driften zu weit auseinander. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "304.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "309.280", 
   "id": "s000097", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Momentan d\u00fcrfen zum Beispiel Schweine 24\u00a0Stunden durchg\u00e4ngig transportiert werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "309.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "312.120", 
   "id": "s000098", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Erst dann muss eine Ruhepause eingelegt werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "312.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "313.080", 
   "id": "s000099", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Forderung der Gr\u00fcnen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "313.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "317.240", 
   "id": "s000100", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "EU-weit die Transportzeiten von Schlachttieren auf acht Stunden zu begrenzen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "317.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "322.440", 
   "id": "s000101", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist richtig und wird immerhin von der Bundesregierung auf EU-Ebene vertreten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "322.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "324.440", 
   "id": "s000102", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber eine Einigung ist noch immer nicht vorhanden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "324.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "327.640", 
   "id": "s000103", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dar\u00fcber hinaus m\u00fcssen \u00c4nderungen an der zul\u00e4ssigen Ladungsdichte\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "327.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "329.000", 
   "id": "s000104", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das wurde schon erw\u00e4hnt\u00a0\u2013, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "329.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "333.360", 
   "id": "s000105", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der Temperaturregelung und der Kontrollwege vorgenommen werden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "333.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "337.240", 
   "id": "s000106", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Einem ausgewachsenen Rind stehen lediglich 1,6\u00a0Quadratmeter zur Verf\u00fcgung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "337.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "341.400", 
   "id": "s000107", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und es darf bei Temperaturen von 0 bis 35\u00a0Grad transportiert werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "341.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "347.320", 
   "id": "s000108", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Oftmals herrschen aber in den Sommermonaten an der bulgarisch-t\u00fcrkischen Grenze \u00fcber 40\u00a0Grad, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "347.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "350.160", 
   "id": "s000109", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und im Winter liegen die Temperaturen weit unter der Frostgrenze. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "350.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "352.520", 
   "id": "s000110", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Ladedichte muss so angepasst werden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "352.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "356.200", 
   "id": "s000111", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass jedes Tier sowohl stehen als auch liegen kann. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "356.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "357.560", 
   "id": "s000112", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es ist schon total elit\u00e4r, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "357.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "361.240", 
   "id": "s000113", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn sich ein Tier w\u00e4hrend dieser ganzen Zeit einmal hinlegen kann."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "361.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "364.440", 
   "id": "s000114", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Notwendig und ein tats\u00e4chlicher Fortschritt w\u00e4re es sicherlich auch, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "364.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "369.360", 
   "id": "s000115", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn die Fahrtrouten der Tiertransporte in Echtzeit an die zust\u00e4ndigen Beh\u00f6rden \u00fcbermittelt w\u00fcrden,"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "369.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "374.600", 
   "id": "s000116", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um Kontrollen effektiver ausgestalten und etwaige Verst\u00f6\u00dfe gegen Transportauflagen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "374.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "376.160", 
   "id": "s000117", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die andauernd stattfinden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "376.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "380.320", 
   "id": "s000118", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "schneller ahnden zu k\u00f6nnen und den Tierschutz dann sofort durchzusetzen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "380.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "389.960", 
   "id": "s000119", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Bislang k\u00f6nnen die Daten n\u00e4mlich nur im Nachhinein ausgewertet und Strafen r\u00fcckwirkend ausgesprochen werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "389.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "397.640", 
   "id": "s000120", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ansonsten k\u00f6nnen die Verst\u00f6\u00dfe weiterhin nur bei punktuellen Kontrollen auf Transportstrecken eher zuf\u00e4llig festgestellt werden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "397.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "400.960", 
   "id": "s000121", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und da werden sehr oft M\u00e4ngel bemerkt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "400.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "403.800", 
   "id": "s000122", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In diesem Zusammenhang m\u00fcssen nicht nur die Fahrer von Tiertransporten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "403.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "405.640", 
   "id": "s000123", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern auch Spediteure und diejenigen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "405.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "407.520", 
   "id": "s000124", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die die Spediteure beauftragen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "407.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "409.800", 
   "id": "s000125", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "mehr in die Verantwortung genommen werden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "409.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "415.560", 
   "id": "s000126", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Kontrollen ausgeweitet und die Verst\u00f6\u00dfe st\u00e4rker geahndet werden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "415.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "418.160", 
   "id": "s000127", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u2013\u00a0Mal ist das ganz richtig."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "418.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "425.360", 
   "id": "s000128", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die EU-Tierschutztransportverordnung r\u00e4umt den nationalen Gesetzgebern ausdr\u00fccklich die M\u00f6glichkeit ein, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "425.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "430.800", 
   "id": "s000129", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "eine strengere und umfassende Regelung in Bezug auf rein innerstaatliche Tiertransporte zu erlassen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "430.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "432.880", 
   "id": "s000130", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deswegen ist es v\u00f6llig unverst\u00e4ndlich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "432.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "440.960", 
   "id": "s000131", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass Bundesminister Christian Schmidt hier in der vergangenen Wahlperiode trotz mehrfacher Aufforderung nicht nur von unserer Fraktion"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "440.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "441.920", 
   "id": "s000132", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u2013\u00a0halten Sie den Ball mal flach\u00a0\u2013"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "441.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "444.280", 
   "id": "s000133", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "v\u00f6llig unt\u00e4tig dabei geblieben ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "444.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "447.120", 
   "id": "s000134", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Transportdauer auf vier Stunden zu begrenzen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "447.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "448.280", 
   "id": "s000135", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn er es nicht macht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "448.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "449.680", 
   "id": "s000136", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dann macht er es nicht."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "449.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "450.200", 
   "id": "s000137", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u2013\u00a0Ja, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "450.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "452.080", 
   "id": "s000138", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das werden Sie auch noch verstehen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "452.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "453.160", 
   "id": "s000139", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es reicht auch nicht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "453.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "457.680", 
   "id": "s000140", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "den zust\u00e4ndigen EU-Kommissar zum Handeln aufzufordern und dann, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "457.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "459.240", 
   "id": "s000141", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie auf meine Anfrage erfolgt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "459.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "460.200", 
   "id": "s000142", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "darzustellen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "460.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "462.680", 
   "id": "s000143", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass man unmittelbar leider nichts machen kann. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "462.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "465.560", 
   "id": "s000144", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Wille zum Handeln hier vor Ort ist entscheidend, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "465.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "467.880", 
   "id": "s000145", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und den konnte ich bislang leider nicht erkennen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "467.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "473.560", 
   "id": "s000146", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wie die Antr\u00e4ge richtigerweise zum Ausdruck bringen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "473.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "478.080", 
   "id": "s000147", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "darf die Verantwortung f\u00fcr unsere Nutztiere nicht einfach an der EU-Au\u00dfengrenze enden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "478.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "481.280", 
   "id": "s000148", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Kann kein artgerechter Umgang mit den Tieren w\u00e4hrend der Transporte, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "481.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "485.800", 
   "id": "s000149", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dem Entladevorgang und insbesondere der Schlachtung in Drittstaaten garantiert werden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "485.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "489.080", 
   "id": "s000150", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "m\u00fcssen Tiertransporte aus Deutschland ausgesetzt werden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "489.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "496.400", 
   "id": "s000151", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Denn auch in anderen Wirtschaftsbereichen gibt es anerkannte innerstaatliche Verantwortung f\u00fcr Handlungen im Ausland. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "496.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "504.120", 
   "id": "s000152", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Denken wir einmal an Endverbleibskontrollen nach Waffenverk\u00e4ufen oder an die Bereiche Bekleidung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "504.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "505.400", 
   "id": "s000153", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Technik, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "505.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "506.240", 
   "id": "s000154", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Tiernahrung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "506.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "508.080", 
   "id": "s000155", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Da muss dann auch einmal nachgeschaut werden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "508.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "509.920", 
   "id": "s000156", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was im Ausland abl\u00e4uft."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "509.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "511.720", 
   "id": "s000157", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wie ich zu Beginn sagte, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "511.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "515.880", 
   "id": "s000158", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "m\u00fcssen sowohl auf europ\u00e4ischer als auch auf nationaler Ebene M\u00f6glichkeiten gepr\u00fcft werden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "515.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "518.680", 
   "id": "s000159", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Tiertransporte durch Fleischtransporte zu ersetzen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "518.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "519.720", 
   "id": "s000160", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Kollegin Mittag, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "519.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "521.440", 
   "id": "s000161", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie m\u00fcssen bitte zum Schluss kommen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "521.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "521.960", 
   "id": "s000162", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sofort.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "521.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "524.680", 
   "id": "s000163", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Denn derartiges Vorgehen der Ziell\u00e4nder kann offenkundig nicht abgestellt werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "524.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "529.000", 
   "id": "s000164", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ausfuhrgenehmigungen werden schlie\u00dflich nicht automatisch erteilt\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "529.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "529.680", 
   "id": "s000165", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "hoffe ich."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "529.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "530.400", 
   "id": "s000166", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Danke sch\u00f6n."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "530.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "540.000", 
   "id": "s000167", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Zu seiner ersten Rede im Bundestag hat der Abgeordnete Thomas Ehrhorn f\u00fcr die AfD-Fraktion das Wort."
   ]
  }
 ]
}